不，他们可能比我们都聪明 谁知道呢？
No, they might be smarter than all of us. Who knows?

862
00:57:29,940 --> 00:57:32,340
他把鱼都赶走了 还在这里慷慨激昂地说废话！
He drove the fish away, now he's ranting this rubbish!

863
00:57:32,510 --> 00:57:35,770
嘿，听我说 别碰我，你这肮脏的寄生虫
Hey, let me tell something to you. Don't touch me, you filthy vermin.

864
00:57:35,940 --> 00:57:37,770
嘿，你干什么 这就是因果联系
Hey, watch it. And so it follows.

865
00:57:37,950 --> 00:57:41,440
异议导致分裂，分裂导致厄运
Dissent leads to division and division leads us to doom.

866
00:57:41,620 --> 00:57:44,680
你，快乐大脚，曼波，必须离开 听听
You, Mumble Happy Feet, must go. Hear, hear.

867
00:57:44,850 --> 00:57:47,290
一步也别动，甜心
Don't you take one step, sweetheart.

868
00:57:47,460 --> 00:57:50,950
你跟这些老糊涂一样有权利呆在这里
You have as much right to be here as any of these daffy old fools.

869
00:57:51,790 --> 00:57:54,390
诺玛・珍，这事我来处理
Norma Jean, I'll deal with this.

870
00:57:54,560 --> 00:57:56,030
爸？
Pa?

871
00:57:58,400 --> 00:58:01,390
曼波，你必须和这些 所谓的朋友断绝关系
Mumble, you must renounce your so-called friends...

872
00:58:01,570 --> 00:58:03,590
并放弃你那些奇怪的想法和特殊的举动
...your peculiar thoughts, your strange ways.

873
00:58:03,770 --> 00:58:05,140
孟菲斯 如果我们是虔诚的…
Memphis. If we are devout...

874
00:58:05,310 --> 00:58:07,430
…并且真诚的祈祷，鱼会回来的
...sincere in our praise, the fish will return.

875
00:58:07,610 --> 00:58:10,870
但是，爸… 听着，孩子，我自己也曾堕落过
But, Pa... Listen, boy, I was a backslider myself.

876
00:58:11,050 --> 00:58:13,310
现在我们正在为我当初的疏忽付出代价
I was careless and now we're paying the price.

877
00:58:13,480 --> 00:58:15,070
这和曼波有什么关系？
What's this got to do with Mumble?

878
00:58:15,250 --> 00:58:18,180
因为我的疏忽他才变成了这个样子 他有什么错？
It's why he is the way he is. There's nothing wrong with him!

879
00:58:18,350 --> 00:58:21,410
面对现实吧，我们的儿子是个异类 他不是异类，明白吗？
Face it, our sors all messed up. He's not messed up, hear me?

880
00:58:21,590 --> 00:58:23,560
相信我，我心里清楚 你怎么能这么说？
Believe me, I know. How can you say that?

881
00:58:23,730 --> 00:58:26,820
因为他还在蛋里时我把它掉地上了
Because when he was just an egg, I dropped him!

882
00:58:26,990 --> 00:58:28,760
孟菲斯
Memphis.

883
00:58:30,600 --> 00:58:32,160
曼波
Mumble.

884
00:58:34,470 --> 00:58:37,030
哦，我可怜的小曼波
Oh, my poor little Mumble.

885
00:58:37,210 --> 00:58:38,870
但是，妈妈，可是我很正常啊
But, Mom, I'm perfectly fine.

886
00:58:39,040 --> 00:58:41,030
不不，你不正常，孩子 没错
No. No, you're not, boy. That's right.

887
00:58:41,210 --> 00:58:44,770
为了我们大家 别再动你那畸形的脚了
For all our sakes, you must stop this freakiness with the feet.

888
00:58:44,950 --> 00:58:49,080
你父亲说得很对 这反映出了他很痛苦但愿意忏悔
Your father speaks wisely. Heed his suffering heart and repent.

889
00:58:49,250 --> 00:58:51,450
但这毫无意义啊
But it just doesn't make any sense.

890
00:58:51,620 --> 00:58:53,680
看来你的狂妄自大让我们没有别的选择了
Then your arrogance leaves us no choice!

891
00:58:53,860 --> 00:58:54,840
别，等等
No, wait.

892
00:58:55,860 --> 00:59:00,120
拜托了，儿子 你可以做到的，不是很难
Please, son, you can do this. It ain't so hard.

893
00:59:02,060 --> 00:59:05,730
别让我改变，爸，我是改变不了的
Don't ask me to change, Pa, because I can't.

894
00:59:10,060 --> 00:59:13,960
大家，不用白费口舌了
And that, my brethren, is the end of it.

895
00:59:14,130 --> 00:59:16,030
你，赶快滚！
You, begone!

896
00:59:18,970 --> 00:59:22,270
曼波 没事的，妈妈，没事的
Mumble. No, Ma, it's okay. It's okay.

897
00:59:23,510 --> 00:59:26,170
你记住了
Let me tell something to you.

898
00:59:26,340 --> 00:59:28,470
当我找到鱼群失踪的原因时…
When I find out what's happening to the fish...

899
00:59:29,350 --> 00:59:31,140
…我会回来的
...I 'll be back.

900
00:59:31,980 --> 00:59:33,610
请让开，请让开
Let me through? Let me through.

901
00:59:33,780 --> 00:59:35,880
曼波，你没必要离开 让他去吧
Mumble, you don't have to go. Let it be.

902
00:59:36,050 --> 00:59:38,520
葛露亚 不，不，爸爸，这不公平
Gloria. No. No, Dad, this isn't fair.

903
00:59:38,690 --> 00:59:40,920
葛露亚，听你爸爸的话
Gloria, listen to your father.

904
00:59:41,430 --> 00:59:46,990
我的亲人总是责难于他
My folks were always putting him down

905
00:59:47,160 --> 00:59:50,030
责难，责难，责难
Down, down, down

906
00:59:50,200 --> 00:59:54,470
他们说他生错了地方
They said he came From the wrong side of town

907
00:59:54,640 --> 00:59:58,130
他生错了地方
He came from the wrong side of town

908
00:59:58,310 --> 01:00:01,400
他们告诉我，他是个冤孽
They told me he was bad

909
01:00:01,580 --> 01:00:02,670
冤孽
So bad

910
01:00:02,850 --> 01:00:06,780
但我知道他很伤心 如此伤心
But I know he was sad So sad

911
01:00:06,950 --> 01:00:12,120
我永远不会忘记他，那个可恶的带头老大
I'll never forget him The leader of the pack

912
01:00:12,290 --> 01:00:16,120
我们的心灵之歌 献给我们真正的朋友，曼波
We sing the heart of our true friend, Mumble.

913
01:00:16,290 --> 01:00:22,290
你们这帮无知、愚蠢、顽固、可悲的企鹅
You are a nation of peeny-weeny, piffling, piccolini, piddly-diddly pouft!

914
01:00:23,530 --> 01:00:25,430
团结才有希望
Together, we prevail.

915
01:00:25,600 --> 01:00:27,470
我们信仰智慧
In the wisdoms, we trust.

916
01:00:27,640 --> 01:00:29,570
我们信仰
We trust.

917
01:00:31,710 --> 01:00:34,540
当心
Look out

918
01:00:34,710 --> 01:00:39,240
当心
Look out

919
01:00:40,050 --> 01:00:43,020
当心
Look out

920
01:00:43,190 --> 01:00:47,820
当…
Look...

921
01:00:47,990 --> 01:00:52,090
当心
Look out

922
01:00:55,770 --> 01:00:59,960
别担心，高个子 我爸爸也叫我，可怜的失败者
Don't worry, tall guy. My father also called me a pitiful loser.

923
01:01:00,140 --> 01:01:01,260
看看我现在
Look how I turn out.

924
01:01:01,440 --> 01:01:02,630
没有用的，雷蒙
You're not helping, Ramon.

925
01:01:02,810 --> 01:01:06,500
他会好起来的 只要找到鱼群到底发生了什么就好办了
He gonna be okay. All he gotta do is find out what happened to the fish.

926
01:01:06,680 --> 01:01:08,650
那他怎么找？ 他已经想到了什么
How he gonna do that? He think of something.

927
01:01:08,810 --> 01:01:10,800
异形 什么？
The aliens. What?

928
01:01:10,980 --> 01:01:13,810
我要去和异形对话 你去哪里找他们？
I'm gonna talk to the aliens. How you gonna find aliens?

929
01:01:13,980 --> 01:01:16,540
爱拉斯 他不喜欢你，一点也不喜欢你
Lovelace. He don't like you. He don't like you at all.

930
01:01:16,720 --> 01:01:18,810
没问题，我会唤醒他善良的本性
That's okay. I'll appeal to his better nature.

931
01:01:18,990 --> 01:01:21,460
怎么唤醒？ 用非同一般的残忍刑罚？
How you gonna do that? Cruel and unusual punishment?

932
01:01:21,630 --> 01:01:24,120
难以想象的拷问？ 还是可以想象的？
Unimaginable torture? Imaginable torture?

933
01:01:24,290 --> 01:01:26,490
你的歌声？ 不是吧！
Your singing? No!

934
01:01:26,660 --> 01:01:29,000
谁能找到我…
"Can anybody find me"...

935
01:01:29,400 --> 01:01:32,060
你把冰都弄裂了 是雪崩！
You're cracking the ice! Avalanche!

936
01:01:32,240 --> 01:01:33,900
没错，好吧，谢谢你
Yes, okay. Thank you.

937
01:01:44,310 --> 01:01:47,220
爱拉斯，你在吗？
Lovelace. You there?

938
01:01:47,380 --> 01:01:49,510
爱拉斯！
Lovelace!

939
01:01:52,390 --> 01:01:54,190
爱拉斯
Lovelace.

940
01:01:59,230 --> 01:02:00,860
爱拉斯？
Lovelace?

941
01:02:01,030 --> 01:02:02,360
来的不是时候？
Is this a bad time?

942
01:02:02,530 --> 01:02:04,470
虽然我们没有预约，但是…
I know we don't have an appointment, but...

943
01:02:04,630 --> 01:02:06,760
就一个问题 我要你直截了当的回答
Just one question and I want a straight answer.

944
01:02:06,940 --> 01:02:08,530
哪里能找到神仙？
Where do I find the mystic beings?

945
01:02:11,370 --> 01:02:13,370
他怎么不说话？
Why don't he speak?

946
01:02:15,380 --> 01:02:18,010
爱拉斯，你没事吧？
Lovelace, you okay?

947
01:02:19,480 --> 01:02:22,680
天，他走火入魔了 是癫痫，癫痫！
Boy, he's possessed. It's a seizure! It's a seizure!

948
01:02:22,850 --> 01:02:24,320
把嘴掰开 抓住他的舌头
Open the beak. Grab his tongue.

949
01:02:24,490 --> 01:02:27,080
他快窒息了 他脖子上的东西太紧了
He's choking. That thing around his neck, it's too tight.

950
01:02:27,260 --> 01:02:29,890
嘿，你怎么不早说 听我数到三
Well, why didn't you say so? On three.

951
01:02:30,060 --> 01:02:34,330
住手！听着！不，朋友们，朋友们！住手！
Stop! Listen! No! Amigos! Amigos! Stop!

952
01:02:34,500 --> 01:02:36,490
干嘛？ 这会弄伤了他
What? You're hurting him.

953
01:02:38,570 --> 01:02:40,040
好些了吗？
Any better?

954
01:02:40,200 --> 01:02:42,730
爱拉斯，你脖子上的那东西哪来的？
Lovelace, how did you get that thing around your neck?

955
01:02:42,910 --> 01:02:46,240
是被安放在他脖子上的 神仙干的
It was bestowed on him. By the mystic beings.

956
01:02:46,410 --> 01:02:48,570
不是他们放的？ 不是
They didn't bestow it? No.

957
01:02:48,750 --> 01:02:51,740
哦，天，他已经语无伦次了
Oh, come on, he don't know what he's saying.

958
01:02:51,920 --> 01:02:54,910
是你在游泳时，不小心被套住的？
You were swimming and it just got caught around your neck.

959
01:02:55,090 --> 01:02:57,990
哦，怎么可能，他可是大师啊
Oh, no way. He the guru.

960
01:02:58,990 --> 01:03:02,190
爱拉斯，你到底见过神仙没有？
Lovelace, did you ever actually meet a mystic being?

961
01:03:02,930 --> 01:03:04,550
正式的见过？
Officially?

962
01:03:06,030 --> 01:03:07,020
没有
No.

963
01:03:07,200 --> 01:03:09,130
我早就知道！全是一派胡言！
I knew it! It's all a lie.

964
01:03:09,300 --> 01:03:11,160
但这肯定是某人的
But this belongs to someone.

965
01:03:11,330 --> 01:03:14,030
要是能找到他们，我敢肯定他们能把它拿下来
If we could find them, I bet you they could take it off.

966
01:03:14,440 --> 01:03:18,670
告诉我你在哪里被套住的 我相信他们会帮助我们的，你和我
Show me where you found it. I'm sure they could help us. You and me both.

967
01:03:21,510 --> 01:03:23,410
两个单词，三个音节
Two words, three syllables.

968
01:03:23,580 --> 01:03:25,380
到底是什么？ 你快死了？
What is it? You're dying?

969
01:03:25,550 --> 01:03:29,250
不不，等等 过去，过去，你过去的生活
No, no, wait. Past, past, your past life.

970
01:03:29,420 --> 01:03:31,010
你在放毒气
You're passing gas.

971
01:03:32,420 --> 01:03:34,410
他现在觉得自己是只海象
Now he thinks he's an elephant seal.

972
01:03:34,590 --> 01:03:36,530
不不不，翻过前面那座山
No, no, no. Go over the mountains.

973
01:03:36,690 --> 01:03:39,630
到山那边去！ 穿过海象的地盘
Go over the mountains! Through the land of the elephant seals.

974
01:03:39,800 --> 01:03:44,390
在海象地盘的另一边 在海象地盘的另一边！
Beyond the land of the elephant seals. Beyond the land of the elephant seals!

975
01:03:55,350 --> 01:03:57,510
等等 怎么了？
Wait. What?

976
01:03:58,420 --> 01:04:00,410
我听到声音了
I hear voices.

977
01:04:00,580 --> 01:04:02,250
有声音 哪里？
There is a voice. Where?

978
01:04:02,420 --> 01:04:05,980
风中有很小的声音 曼波！
There's a little voice on the wind. Mumble!

979
01:04:06,160 --> 01:04:07,450
“曼波”？ “曼波”？
"Mambo"? "Mambo"?

980
01:04:07,620 --> 01:04:09,060
听 快乐大脚，曼波
Listen. Mumble Happy Feet.

981
01:04:09,590 --> 01:04:10,820
葛露亚？ 葛露亚！
Gloria? Gloria!

982
01:04:10,990 --> 01:04:11,980
葛露亚？
Gloria?

983
01:04:12,160 --> 01:04:14,690
嘿，来了个追随者 你会被她弄得神魂颠倒的，兄弟
Hey, you got a stalker. She's obsessed with you, man.

984
01:04:18,300 --> 01:04:20,770
真不敢相信是你
I can't believe it's you.

985
01:04:20,940 --> 01:04:23,000
当然是我了
Of course it's me.

986
01:04:24,310 --> 01:04:26,000
你来这干嘛？
What are you doing here?

987
01:04:26,180 --> 01:04:29,370
这世上的爱永不消失
All the love in the world can't be gone

988
01:04:29,550 --> 01:04:33,410
爱的需要永远没错
All the need to be loved can't be wrong

989
01:04:33,580 --> 01:04:36,310
噢，天 往哪走，“闪亮的大脚”？
Oh, my. So which way, twinkletoes?

990
01:04:36,490 --> 01:04:39,850
不不不，你要是跟来了 也许永远也回不去了
No, no, no. If you come, you may never get back home.

991
01:04:40,020 --> 01:04:41,390
我不在乎
Fine by me.

992
01:04:41,560 --> 01:04:47,020
葛露亚，那边有你自己的生活 我不能，我是说，我们不能，在这里…
Gloria, you have a life back there. I don't. I mean, we don't. Not out here.

993
01:04:47,200 --> 01:04:50,290
我们怎么能保证蛋宝宝的安全？ 我是说如果我们生了一个的话…
How can we keep an egg safe? That's if we ever had an egg.

994
01:04:50,470 --> 01:04:53,060
这个，我不要蛋宝宝也能很快乐啊
Well, I don't need an egg to be happy.

995
01:04:53,240 --> 01:04:57,260
你现在是这么说 但以后你的朋友们都有了的时候呢？
You say that now, but what about later when all your friends have eggs?

996
01:04:58,640 --> 01:04:59,870
我还有你
Then I'll have you.

997
01:05:01,310 --> 01:05:04,710
他要开始山盟海誓了
Now he's going to pledge his soul forever.

998
01:05:04,880 --> 01:05:06,010
葛露亚 瞧，来了
Gloria. Here it comes.

999
01:05:06,180 --> 01:05:13,110
我是那种比较特殊的人 需要自己空间的那种
I'm a particular kind of guy, the kind of guy who needs his own space.

1000
01:05:13,390 --> 01:05:15,260
不是针对你，而是我…
It's not you, it's me.

1001
01:05:15,430 --> 01:05:17,860
我只是还没打算开始认真的恋爱
I'm just not up for a serious relationship right now.

1002
01:05:18,030 --> 01:05:21,360
他现在在试着赶她走，继续看
What he's trying to do now is he's pushing her away. Let's watch.

1003
01:05:21,530 --> 01:05:25,020
不管你说什么，做什么 我是跟定你了
No matter what you say or do, you're stuck with me.

1004
01:05:25,200 --> 01:05:28,300
拜托，别装了 好像我来这里你一点都不激动似的
Oh, come on. As if you're not totally thrilled that I'm here.

1005
01:05:28,470 --> 01:05:31,930
她开始用美人计了 看，这就是你的问题
Now she got him on the ropes. See, right there is your problem.

1006
01:05:32,110 --> 01:05:34,010
你觉得你的魅力谁也无法抗拒，是吧？
You think you're irresistible, don't you?

1007
01:05:34,180 --> 01:05:36,510
我不管你从哪里学来的 听了这话的人一定很受伤
I don't care where you're from, that's got to hurt.

1008
01:05:36,680 --> 01:05:39,410
你刚刚说什么？ 葛露亚是如此的高贵，如此的有天分
Excuse me? Gloria's so gorgeous, Gloria's so talented.

1009
01:05:39,580 --> 01:05:40,570
什么？
What?

1010
01:05:40,750 --> 01:05:43,150
你只不过能飙到几个高音而已
Just because you can hit a few high notes.

1011
01:05:43,320 --> 01:05:45,450
你对我的歌声有意见？
You got a problem with my singing?

1012
01:05:45,620 --> 01:05:47,850
不是，你唱得相当地好
No, it's perfectly fine.

1013
01:05:48,020 --> 01:05:49,890
“好”？ 如果你喜欢这样赞美你的话
"Fine"? If you like that sort of thing.

1014
01:05:50,060 --> 01:05:52,650
我早已不喜欢这么幼稚的东西了 什么？
It's a little Nana Tootsie for my taste. What?

1015
01:05:52,830 --> 01:05:54,960
你知道的 炫耀，浮华，沙沙声
You know, showy, flashy, froufrou.

1016
01:05:55,130 --> 01:05:56,620
“沙沙声”？ 没错
"Froufrou"? That's right.

1017
01:05:56,800 --> 01:06:00,930
不知道你从哪里学的，认为这种 上蹿下跳，原地乱颠的动作很“酷”
Coming from someone who thinks it's cool to jig up and down really fast on the spot...

1018
01:06:01,100 --> 01:06:03,370
…就像个抽筋的白痴似的
...like some twitchy idiot.

1019
01:06:07,140 --> 01:06:09,770
你这个固执己见、不可理喻的傻瓜！
You stubborn, hippity-hoppity fool!

1020
01:06:09,950 --> 01:06:11,810
就站在你后面
Right back at you.

1021
01:06:22,160 --> 01:06:24,650
朋友，干得不错
Amigo, that was a good thing you do.

1022
01:06:24,830 --> 01:06:27,090
她不和你在一起，会过的好得多
She is going to be so much better off without you.

1023
01:06:27,260 --> 01:06:30,390
她会去找一个善良的，站得稳的家伙 来安慰她…
She is going to find a good, steady guy to comfort her...

1024
01:06:30,570 --> 01:06:33,760
…来深爱她，和她生一大堆宝宝
...and love her up real good and raise a big family.

1025
01:06:33,940 --> 01:06:36,170
雷蒙 然后忘记这段感情…
Ramon. And then she's going to let herself go...

1026
01:06:36,340 --> 01:06:39,470
雷蒙 他在心痛呢，非常心痛
Ramon. He's hurting. He's hurting bad.

1027
01:06:39,640 --> 01:06:44,310
噢，听着，听着 憋在心里会疯的，你得把它们宣泄出来
Oh, listen, listen, don't hold it in or you explode. You got to let it out.

1028
01:06:44,480 --> 01:06:47,180
宣泄吧，宣泄吧
You just let it out. You let it out.

1029
01:06:47,350 --> 01:06:50,220
你们几个转过身去一会儿
Everybody, turn away for a moment.

1030
01:06:50,390 --> 01:06:52,690
如果她现在离开他
If she leave him now

1031
01:06:52,860 --> 01:06:58,060
他就失去了最宝贵的东西
She take away the biggest part of him

1032
01:07:00,430 --> 01:07:02,360
不要啊，宝贝，请不要离开
Don't, baby, please, don't go

1033
01:07:02,530 --> 01:07:04,400
拜托，伙计们
Please, guys.

1034
01:07:04,570 --> 01:07:06,560
别再唱了
No more singing.

1035
01:07:17,150 --> 01:07:19,810
然后她跟我说“够了，你让我感到恶心”
Then she say to me, "Enough, you are making me nauseous."

1036
01:07:19,980 --> 01:07:23,710
然后我闭嘴了，差点发怒 接着她说什么你知道吗？
So I become silent, almost moody, and you know what she says?

1037
01:07:23,890 --> 01:07:25,950
“你从不让他人替你分担你要学会宣泄出来”
"You never share. You got to let it out."

1038
01:07:26,120 --> 01:07:28,890
雷蒙，你又来了 宣泄吧，宣泄吧
Ramon, come on. Let it out. Let it out.

1039
01:07:29,060 --> 01:07:30,490
停下！放手吧
Stop it! Let it go.

1040
01:07:30,660 --> 01:07:34,320
我这辈子没有遇到过一段美好的感情 拥抱他一下吧，拥抱一下
I never had a good relationship in my life. Give him a hug. Give him a hug.

1041
01:07:34,500 --> 01:07:35,730
我要宣泄！ 又来了
I let it out! There we go.

1042
01:07:35,900 --> 01:07:38,460
我要宣泄！ 我知道，要学会忘记
I let it out. I know. Get over it.

1043
01:07:38,640 --> 01:07:41,430
你还能走吗？ 嗯
Can you keep going? Yeah.

1044
01:07:41,600 --> 01:07:44,800
什么味道？ 不是我
What's that smell? It wasn't me.

1045
01:07:45,940 --> 01:07:49,710
嘿，毛球，是我们跟着你 走啊，快爬上来
Hey, Fluffy, we're following you. Get up here.

1046
01:07:57,850 --> 01:08:01,920
这些海象 他们不吃企鹅的，对吧？
So these elephant seals, they're not penguin eaters, are they?

1047
01:08:02,090 --> 01:08:04,490
我不知道，我相信他们是食草动物
I don't know. I believe they are herbivores.

1048
01:08:04,660 --> 01:08:06,530
什么？ 我是说，他们只吃海藻
What? You know, kelp-suckers.

1049
01:08:06,700 --> 01:08:09,030
来吧，爱拉斯，跳
Here we go, Lovelace. Come on.

1050
01:08:10,700 --> 01:08:12,570
赶紧跳，赶紧跳
Jump in time. Jump in time.

1051
01:08:12,740 --> 01:08:15,500
好吧，我们跳吧 好，好，好，准备好了？
Okay, let's do it. Okay, okay, okay. Ready?

1052
01:08:18,710 --> 01:08:21,110
我知道我能行，我得骗一下自己
I can do this. I can do this. I got to trick myself.

1053
01:08:21,280 --> 01:08:23,180
瞧，那是什么？
Boy, look at that. What?

1054
01:08:39,130 --> 01:08:43,690
你们这些野小子最好是迷路了 否则入侵别人的领地可是犯罪
You blokes better be lost, because trespassing's a crime.

1055
01:08:43,870 --> 01:08:47,860
我们只是路过 对，他带我们来的
We're just passing through. Yeah. We're with him.

1056
01:08:48,470 --> 01:08:50,940
你们不会是想翻过远处那些山…
You wouldn't be heading over them distant hills...

1057
01:08:51,110 --> 01:08:53,040
…再穿过那些暴风雪的土地吧？
...and through the blizzard country?

1058
01:08:53,210 --> 01:08:56,010
如果这是通往禁闭海滩的唯一通路 那么是的
If it's the only way to the forbidden shore, yeah.

1059
01:08:56,180 --> 01:08:57,370
哎呀
Crikey.

1060
01:08:57,550 --> 01:09:01,040
你们会碰到毁灭者的
You might come face to face with an annihilator.

1061
01:09:01,220 --> 01:09:02,240
异形毁灭者？
An alien annihilator?

1062
01:09:02,420 --> 01:09:05,350
没错，一看到它你们就会被切成两半
Too right. Cut you up as soon as look at you.

1063
01:09:05,520 --> 01:09:08,550
它们经过的地方不留活口
Waste every living thing in their path.

1064
01:09:08,730 --> 01:09:10,390
他们也毁灭鱼群吗？
Could they be annihilating the fish?

1065
01:09:10,560 --> 01:09:12,150
所有生物
Every living thing.

1066
01:09:12,330 --> 01:09:14,800
太残忍了，兄弟，太残忍了
Merciless, mate. Merciless.

1067
01:09:14,960 --> 01:09:17,260
即使你是庞大的巨鲸…
Even if you're a whopping great whale...

1068
01:09:17,430 --> 01:09:20,100
…也会被他们拉上岸…
...they drag your sorry carcass ashore...

1069
01:09:20,270 --> 01:09:25,970
…切成块，化成汤 变为他们享受的食物…
...dice you up, melt you down, and turn you into fun food.

1070
01:09:26,140 --> 01:09:28,410
前一刻你还是一头巨鲸…
One day you're a big old whale...

1071
01:09:28,580 --> 01:09:30,880
…后一刻…
...next minute...

1072
01:09:31,050 --> 01:09:32,450
…就变成享受的食物了
...fun food.

1073
01:09:32,620 --> 01:09:34,050
得有人去阻止他们
Someone's gotta stop them.

1074
01:09:34,220 --> 01:09:36,710
哦，是吗？你想用什么方法？
Oh, yeah? What's gonna be your approach?

1075
01:09:36,890 --> 01:09:38,910
如果我能和他们谈谈的话
If I could just talk to them.

1076
01:09:39,090 --> 01:09:40,580
唤醒他们善良的本性
Appeal to their better nature.

1077
01:09:40,760 --> 01:09:41,750
很好
Beauty.

1078
01:09:41,930 --> 01:09:47,520
当你那些小把戏得逞的时候 一定要让我们知道，记住了吗？
When that crafty little trick pays off, you be sure to let us know, won't you?

1079
01:09:47,700 --> 01:09:50,560
好吧，爱拉斯，我们走
All right, Lovelace, let's go.

1080
01:09:52,800 --> 01:09:54,900
再见，爱拉斯
See you, Lovelace.

1081
01:09:57,340 --> 01:09:59,770
那边会是你的墓地，伙计
Your funeral, mate.

1082
01:10:47,590 --> 01:10:50,150
噢，天
Oh, man!

1083
01:10:51,190 --> 01:10:53,920
用力推啊 好
Push tight. Okay.

1084
01:11:08,580 --> 01:11:10,740
来啊，伙计们，加油！
Come on, guys. Let's do it.

1085
01:11:10,910 --> 01:11:14,820
你们能行的，快点，推啊
You can do it. Come on, push!

1086
01:11:59,060 --> 01:12:01,090
什么声音？
What's that noise?

1087
01:12:02,630 --> 01:12:03,830
没听见啊
There's no noise.

1088
01:12:04,000 --> 01:12:06,560
没有喘气，也没有呼吸 爱拉斯呢？
No gasping. No wheezing. Where's Lovelace?

1089
01:12:08,640 --> 01:12:13,410
有时候一只勇敢的企鹅也会失足而死
Sometimes a brave penguin will just slip away to die.

1090
01:12:13,580 --> 01:12:15,510
你觉得他会去极乐世界吗？
Do you think he went to a happy place?

1091
01:12:15,680 --> 01:12:19,270
也许吧 不，不，我想他往这边去了
Probably. No, no. I think he went this way.

1092
01:12:31,330 --> 01:12:33,820
来吧，我们走
Come on. Let's go.

1093
01:12:50,410 --> 01:12:52,310
爱拉斯！
Lovelace!

1094
01:12:53,480 --> 01:12:55,970
爱拉斯！
Lovelace!

1095
01:13:02,020 --> 01:13:03,860
哈罗！
Hello?

1096
01:13:05,260 --> 01:13:06,660
有人吗？
Is there anyone there?

1097
01:13:06,830 --> 01:13:10,420
别…别大声喊 小心被人听见
No... No need to shout. Somebody might hear you.

1098
01:13:16,070 --> 01:13:17,840
脚印看起来不大正常
His feet don't look too good.

1099
01:13:18,010 --> 01:13:20,600
他在这里休息了一下 然后他用腹部滑下去了
He rested here. Now he's on his belly!

1100
01:13:20,780 --> 01:13:23,340
不，这边 不知道他在这里做什么
No, this way. You don't want to know what he did here.

1101
01:13:23,510 --> 01:13:25,740
你是对的 他在那！爱拉斯！
You're right. There he is. Lovelace!

1102
01:13:25,920 --> 01:13:29,210
没错！爱拉斯！ 爱拉斯！
All right! Lovelace! Lovelace!

1103
01:13:31,990 --> 01:13:33,750
看看爱拉斯 我们来了
Oh, look at Lovelace. We're here.

1104
01:13:33,920 --> 01:13:37,480
你还好吗？ 伙计，要撑住啊
Are you okay? Come on, man. Hang in there, buddy.

1105
01:13:38,360 --> 01:13:39,990
那是什么？
What is it?

1106
01:13:40,160 --> 01:13:43,430
看，似乎每人都有一个
Oh, look. There's one for everyone.

1107
01:13:43,600 --> 01:13:46,120
坚持住，爱拉斯 我知道他们就在附近
Hang in there, Lovelace. I know they're here somewhere.

1108
01:13:46,300 --> 01:13:48,830
他们为什么把这些东西都留在这里？ 我不知道
Why would they leave all this behind? I don't know.

1109
01:13:49,840 --> 01:13:50,830
嘿
Hey.

1110
01:13:51,010 --> 01:13:53,270
告诉他们我们没有危险 我们没有危险！
Tell them we come in peace. We come in peace!

1111
01:13:53,440 --> 01:13:54,970
爱拉斯 爱拉斯
Lovelace. Lovelace.

1112
01:13:55,140 --> 01:13:56,610
爱拉斯 哦，伙计，坚持住
Lovelace. Oh, buddy, come on.

1113
01:13:56,780 --> 01:13:58,840
你没事吧？ 坚持住，伙计
Are you okay? Hang in there, buddy.

1114
01:14:01,450 --> 01:14:03,920
哦，看起来不大妙 保持冷静
Oh, that's not good. Stay calm.

1115
01:14:04,090 --> 01:14:05,380
保持冷静 不对劲
Stay calm. That's not good.

1116
01:14:05,560 --> 01:14:08,150
好吧，别冷静了 我好怕！
Okay, don't stay calm! Panic!

1117
01:14:14,860 --> 01:14:16,830
噢，不，不！
Oh, no, no!

1118
01:14:18,870 --> 01:14:21,960
哦，它们在玩我们呢 他们在玩我们！
Oh, they're making us appe-teasers. They're appe-teasing us!

1119
01:14:22,140 --> 01:14:24,270
我们都死定了
We're all gonna die.

1120
01:14:25,540 --> 01:14:27,410
无论怎样，都离水远点！
Whatever you do, stay out of the water!

1121
01:14:27,580 --> 01:14:29,700
离水远点 别掉下去！
Stay out of the water. Don't go in the water!

1122
01:14:29,880 --> 01:14:32,580
爱拉斯，别下去！
Lovelace, don't go in the water!

1123
01:14:38,420 --> 01:14:39,950
爱拉斯，坚持住！
Lovelace, hang in there!

1124
01:14:40,120 --> 01:14:42,020
坚持住！
Hang in there!

1125
01:14:43,390 --> 01:14:46,380
把你恶心的舌头拿开！
Get your dirty tongue off him!

1126
01:14:48,800 --> 01:14:50,700
不，不，不！
No, no, no!

1127
01:14:50,870 --> 01:14:52,330
离水远点！
Stay out of the water!

1128
01:14:52,500 --> 01:14:54,200
曼波！ 曼波！
Mumble! Mumble!

1129
01:15:24,470 --> 01:15:29,060
他们在打鸟毛球吗？ 不，这是表演，晚餐和表演
They playing birdminton? No, it's a show. Dinner and a show.

1130
01:15:32,710 --> 01:15:35,270
爱拉斯！
Lovelace!

1131
01:15:40,780 --> 01:15:42,770
好极了！
Rejoice!

1132
01:15:51,490 --> 01:15:52,390
爱拉斯！
Lovelace!

1133
01:15:52,560 --> 01:15:54,620
救命！伸出手来！
Help! Reach out!

1134
01:15:54,800 --> 01:15:56,630
谢谢你，兄弟，谢谢！
Thank you, my brother, thank you!

1135
01:16:07,610 --> 01:16:09,480
我不怕，我不怕！
I wasn't scared! I wasn't scared!

1136
01:16:10,280 --> 01:16:14,220
哦，我可爱的兄弟 谢谢，谢谢，谢谢，谢谢
Oh, my beautiful brother, thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you!

1137
01:16:18,390 --> 01:16:21,360
爱拉斯！你太强了！ 冲，冲
Go, Lovelace! You the man! Go, go, go, go, go!

1138
01:16:21,520 --> 01:16:23,990
够了！
Enough!

1139
01:16:24,160 --> 01:16:26,250
你们今天算是倒霉了！
It's a bad day for you!

1140
01:16:26,430 --> 01:16:28,490
你们在和爱拉斯过招！
You dealing with Lovelace now!

1141
01:16:28,660 --> 01:16:31,330
还有我的人，曼波，也在这儿 告诉他们，爱拉斯
And my man, Mumble, here. You tell them, Lovelace.

1142
01:16:31,500 --> 01:16:34,260
给我滚，死鱼们！拜拜啦
Begone, demon fish. Adios.

1143
01:16:35,670 --> 01:16:37,300
没错
That's right.

1144
01:16:37,470 --> 01:16:39,240
逃回你妈妈那里去吧
You hightail it back to your mamas.

1145
01:16:39,540 --> 01:16:41,600
他是怎么做到的？ 别让我下水去追你们
How did he do that? Don't make me come in the water.

1146
01:16:41,780 --> 01:16:43,710
我不会放过你们的孩子
I'll come after your sons and daughters.

1147
01:16:43,880 --> 01:16:45,870
我不会给你们好脸色的
I'm gonna give you the bad eye.

1148
01:17:40,170 --> 01:17:41,500
他们人好多啊
A whole bunch of them.

1149
01:17:41,670 --> 01:17:44,300
他们想统治世界
They gonna rule the world.

1150
01:17:44,470 --> 01:17:45,460
一定就是他们了
It's gotta be them.

1151
01:17:45,640 --> 01:17:48,910
就算是，我也不想了解 他们甚至都不知道我们的存在
If it is, I don't wanna know about it. They don't even know we exist.

1152
01:17:49,080 --> 01:17:50,410
这么跟你说吧
Let me tell something to you.

1153
01:17:50,580 --> 01:17:53,570
这事到此为止，结束了
This is the end of the road. It's over.

1154
01:17:53,750 --> 01:17:56,650
你已经做了企鹅能做的一切
You did everything penguinly possible.

1155
01:17:56,820 --> 01:17:59,290
你找到了异形 我们会帮你作证的
You found the aliens. We gonna testify to that.

1156
01:17:59,460 --> 01:18:02,820
我们会告诉，你那个可笑的民族 他们对你的看法是完全错误的
We'll tell your whole laughing-boy nation they were dead wrong about you.

1157
01:18:02,990 --> 01:18:04,790
现在我们都回家吧，赶紧走
Now, let's all go back home. Right now.

1158
01:18:04,960 --> 01:18:06,330
好极了
Right on.

1159
01:18:06,500 --> 01:18:08,090
能帮我个忙吗？ 当然
Could I ask a favor of you? Sure.

1160
01:18:08,260 --> 01:18:10,820
什么忙？ 你们能照顾好葛露亚吗？
What kind of favor? Could you make sure Gloria's okay?

1161
01:18:11,000 --> 01:18:12,370
还有我妈妈 什么？
And my ma. What?

1162
01:18:12,540 --> 01:18:14,130
还有，如果看到我爸…
And if you see Pa...

1163
01:18:14,300 --> 01:18:17,170
…告诉他我尽力了
...tell him I tried.

1164
01:18:17,340 --> 01:18:18,830
好吧，不过你到底想说什么？
Okay, what you talking about?

1165
01:18:19,010 --> 01:18:20,770
我要去阻止他们捕我们的鱼
I'm gonna stop them taking our fish.

1166
01:18:20,940 --> 01:18:22,500
你怎么阻止，曼波？
How you gonna do that, Mumble?

1167
01:18:24,880 --> 01:18:27,940
一路平安，朋友！
Adios, amigos!

1168
01:18:28,280 --> 01:18:29,770
朋友！他真去了！
Amigo! He did it.

1169
01:18:53,340 --> 01:18:54,370
你敢相信吗？
You believe that?

1170
01:18:54,540 --> 01:18:58,100
我们怎么跟他妈妈交代？ 他这么大老远带我们来这里，就是为了自杀？
How we gonna tell his mama he bring us all this way just to kill himself?

1171
01:18:58,280 --> 01:19:01,040
不，他没自杀，看
No. He didn't. Look.

1172
01:19:01,880 --> 01:19:03,650
他真是个疯子
He loco maniac.

1173
01:19:03,820 --> 01:19:06,750
历史上第一只会飞的企鹅
First ever flying flipper bird.

1174
01:19:06,920 --> 01:19:09,080
你觉得他有多高？
How tall you think that tall boy was?

1175
01:19:09,260 --> 01:19:12,420
谁能回答？ 比任何人都高
Who could say? Taller than anyone.

1176
01:19:12,600 --> 01:19:16,530
嘿，是我，爱拉斯…
Hey, it's me, Lovelace...

1177
01:19:16,700 --> 01:19:19,100
…也就是以前大家所说的“大师”
...formerly known as "guru."

1178
01:19:19,270 --> 01:19:22,260
我会把你，快乐大脚的故事…
I'm gonna be telling your story, Happy Feet...

1179
01:19:22,440 --> 01:19:26,310
…世世代代将给子孙们听！
...long after you dead and gone!

1180
01:19:43,330 --> 01:19:45,590
嘿，嘿！
Hey! Hey!

1181
01:20:35,740 --> 01:20:38,440
由于被人类的无动于衷所激怒…
Enraged by their indifference...

1182
01:20:38,610 --> 01:20:43,950
…即使他们已在视野中消失已久 他仍然执着地跟随着他们
...he followed them long after they were gone from his sight.

1183
01:20:46,120 --> 01:20:50,350
他探险比我们之中任何一个去过的都远…
He ventured further than any of us had gone before...

1184
01:20:50,530 --> 01:20:54,360
…已经超出了生还的希望
...beyond all hope of return.

1185
01:20:55,300 --> 01:20:57,730
伴随着巨大的洋流…
Swept up by the great currents...

1186
01:20:57,900 --> 01:21:02,560
…他被带着穿过了无尽广阔的大海…
...he was carried endlessly across vast oceans...

1187
01:21:02,740 --> 01:21:06,440
…去向了那未知的世界
...to worlds unknown.

1188
01:22:02,730 --> 01:22:05,500
打扰一下，请问这是哪里？
Excuse me. What is this place?

1189
01:22:05,670 --> 01:22:08,660
你在天堂，大卫，企鹅的天堂
You're in heaven, Dave. Penguin heaven.

1190
01:22:08,840 --> 01:22:10,830
这里离帝企鹅的领地近吗？
Is it anywhere near Emperor Land?

1191
01:22:11,010 --> 01:22:13,800
你可以把这里当作任何地方
It's wherever you want it to be.

1192
01:22:14,640 --> 01:22:18,670
试试水吧，戴夫，完全真实
Try the water, Dave. It's really real.

1193
01:22:34,760 --> 01:22:39,130
我听说，他最终近距离看到的异形…
I heard tell, when he finally saw aliens up close...

1194
01:22:39,300 --> 01:22:43,500
…跟贼鸥描述的一模一样
...they were just as the skua had described.

1195
01:22:43,670 --> 01:22:46,300
请问，你们为什么抢走我们的鱼？
Excuse me. Why are you taking our fish?

1196
01:22:46,480 --> 01:22:51,780
大而丑陋的企鹅 肥胖松弛的脸上没有羽毛
Big, ugly penguins without feathers on their fat, flabby faces.

1197
01:22:51,950 --> 01:22:57,680
你们为什么抢走我们的鱼？ 你们这样会害死我们的
Why are you taking our fish? You're kind of killing us out there.

1198
01:23:00,060 --> 01:23:02,150
不！不，等等！
No! No, wait!

1199
01:23:11,770 --> 01:23:13,740
噢，天
Oh, my.

1200
01:23:14,800 --> 01:23:18,970
哈罗，这是来自帝企鹅领地的问候 下午好
Hello. Hello from Emperor Land. Good afternoon.

1201
01:23:19,140 --> 01:23:20,900
你们为什么抢走我们的鱼？
Why are you taking our fish?

1202
01:23:21,080 --> 01:23:25,510
我知道你们不是故意的 但你们给我们带来了很大的伤害
I'm sure you don't mean to, but you're causing an awful lot of grief.

1203
01:23:26,520 --> 01:23:30,510
我说的不够明白吗？ 都是大白话啊
Am I not making myself clear? I'm speaking plain penguin.

1204
01:23:31,420 --> 01:23:34,980
企鹅语，你们听不懂吗？ 你们在偷我们的鱼
Penguin! Don't you understand? You're stealing our fish.

1205
01:23:39,260 --> 01:23:41,990
噢，拜托，你们谁跟我说话吧
Oh, please, anyone, talk to me!

1206
01:23:42,160 --> 01:23:44,390
可怜可怜我们吧 你们在偷我们的鱼…
For pity's sake, you're stealing our F-l-S...

1207
01:23:49,170 --> 01:23:53,940
三天以后，他已经声嘶力竭
After three days, he would lose his voice.

1208
01:23:54,110 --> 01:23:56,540
三个月以后…
After three months...

1209
01:23:58,510 --> 01:24:02,640
…他几乎忘了他来这里的目的
...he would all but lose his mind.

1210
01:24:15,060 --> 01:24:18,030
你终于找到鱼了，宝贝
So you found the fish, baby.

1211
01:24:19,130 --> 01:24:20,800
妈？
Ma?

1212
01:24:20,970 --> 01:24:22,270
嗨，亲爱的 妈
Hi, sweetie. Ma.

1213
01:24:22,440 --> 01:24:26,840
毛球，不管他们说什么，做什么 我们都会和你站在一起的
Fluffy, no matter what they say or do, we never stopped believing in you.

1214
01:24:27,010 --> 01:24:29,100
那么你很快就能回来了，是吗？
So you'll be back soon, right?

1215
01:24:29,280 --> 01:24:30,910
嘿，别问了，让他吃吧
Hey, come on. Let him eat.

1216
01:24:31,080 --> 01:24:33,070
吃吧，戴夫，不用管我们
Go ahead, Dave. Don't mind us.

1217
01:24:33,580 --> 01:24:35,050
但有很多鱼啊，够大家吃的
But there's plenty for everyone.

1218
01:24:35,220 --> 01:24:37,520
没事的，甜心，我们可以等
It's okay, sugar. We can wait.

1219
01:24:37,690 --> 01:24:39,520
不，不，妈！妈！
No, no, Ma! Ma!

1220
01:24:39,690 --> 01:24:43,090
这里有很多啊，妈！
There's lots here. Ma!

1221
01:24:47,030 --> 01:24:48,620
妈！
Ma!

1222
01:27:08,840 --> 01:27:11,530
孩子，这个你一定得看看 他又开始了
Kids, you gotta see this. He's on now.

1223
01:27:33,300 --> 01:27:35,660
嘿，大家好！
Hey! Hello!

1224
01:27:38,100 --> 01:27:40,660
这不是那个脚有毛病的家伙吗？ 看起来像
Isn't that the fellow with the wacky feet? Looks like.

1225
01:27:40,840 --> 01:27:43,130
他叫什么？ 我以为他死了呢
What was his name? I thought he was dead.

1226
01:27:43,310 --> 01:27:44,700
大家… 显然没死
Everybody... Apparently not.

1227
01:27:44,870 --> 01:27:47,810
大家听着！我有重大消息
Everybody, listen up! I've got big news.

1228
01:27:48,140 --> 01:27:50,130
我知道鱼被谁抢走了
I know who's taking the fish!

1229
01:27:50,310 --> 01:27:52,780
对，然后把他的脑子也挖走了 是那些异形
Yeah, and they took his brain. It's the aliens.

1230
01:27:52,950 --> 01:27:55,210
我跟他们联系了 疯子回来了
I made contact with them. The lunatic is back.

1231
01:27:55,380 --> 01:27:57,380
是异形抢走了我们的鱼
The aliens are taking our fish.

1232
01:27:57,550 --> 01:27:59,610
赶快叫人去把诺亚和长老们请来
Someone ought to fetch Noah and the elders.

1233
01:27:59,790 --> 01:28:01,090
嘿，你
Hey, you.

1234
01:28:01,660 --> 01:28:03,220
葛露亚
Gloria.

1235
01:28:03,390 --> 01:28:05,490
再看到你，觉得有点怪怪的
Kind of weird, seeing you again.

1236
01:28:05,990 --> 01:28:06,980
是啊
Yeah.

1237
01:28:07,160 --> 01:28:09,530
没什么事吧，宝贝 你记得西摩吧
Everything cool here, baby? You remember Seymour.

1238
01:28:09,700 --> 01:28:11,000
当然，嗨，西摩
Yeah. Hi, Seymour.

1239
01:28:11,170 --> 01:28:12,660
嗯
Yeah.

1240
01:28:13,970 --> 01:28:15,700
哪个是你孩子？
So which one is yours?

1241
01:28:16,940 --> 01:28:18,200
全都是
All of them.

1242
01:28:20,580 --> 01:28:24,710
这是我们的歌唱班 他教韵律，我教蓝调
This is our singing class. He teaches rhythm. I teach the blues.

1243
01:28:24,880 --> 01:28:27,470
那你们没…？ 我想我还没等到属于我的那支歌
So you're not? I guess I never heard the right song.

1244
01:28:27,650 --> 01:28:30,780
太好了！我不是那个意思…
That's great! I didn't mean...

1245
01:28:31,120 --> 01:28:32,710
我知道谁抢走了我们的鱼了
I found out who's taking the fish.

1246
01:28:32,890 --> 01:28:35,020
他们很大，有点丑 但是，葛露亚…
They're big and kind of ugly, but, Gloria...

1247
01:28:35,190 --> 01:28:37,490
…他们很厉害的 他们要来这儿
...the things they can do. They're coming here.

1248
01:28:37,660 --> 01:28:38,790
哦，是么？
Oh, is that so?

1249
01:28:38,960 --> 01:28:41,360
他们马上要来了 我想他们是想帮助我们
They'll be here soon. I think they wanna help us.

1250
01:28:41,530 --> 01:28:43,260
那你跟他们谈过了？
So now you speak with them?

1251
01:28:43,430 --> 01:28:46,630
这个，他们不说企鹅语 但他们对这个有反应
Well, they don't speak penguin, but they seem to respond to this.

1252
01:28:46,800 --> 01:28:48,860
他在干嘛？ 开玩笑吧
What's he doing? You gotta be kidding me.

1253
01:28:49,040 --> 01:28:52,060
我建议大家都这么做 这真的很吸引他们
I suggest we all do it. It really gets their attention.

1254
01:28:52,240 --> 01:28:53,570
怎么会这样呢？
And why would it do that?

1255
01:28:53,740 --> 01:28:56,640
你问住我了，不过真的有用
Beats me, but it works.

1256
01:28:56,810 --> 01:28:59,680
嘿，是那个脚抽筋的家伙 怪脚！
Hey, it's the hippity-hopper. Freaky feet!

1257
01:28:59,850 --> 01:29:00,840
孩子们，孩子们…
Boys, boys...

1258
01:29:01,020 --> 01:29:02,010
毛球 高个子
Fluffy. Tall guy.

1259
01:29:02,180 --> 01:29:04,180
兄弟 朋友！
Stretch! Amigo!

1260
01:29:07,790 --> 01:29:10,660
你还敢回来？
So you dare come back?

1261
01:29:10,960 --> 01:29:13,550
他说他找到异形了 是他们抢走了我们的鱼
He says he's found aliens and they're taking our fish.

1262
01:29:13,730 --> 01:29:16,250
他说他们要来了 还让我们都这么做
He says that they're coming and we all have to do this.

1263
01:29:17,730 --> 01:29:21,260
这世上没有异形这东西！
There be no such thing as aliens!

1264
01:29:23,370 --> 01:29:26,100
曼波，转过去
Mumble, turn around.

1265
01:29:29,240 --> 01:29:30,730
这是病变啊
It's a disease.

1266
01:29:31,150 --> 01:29:32,840
这是他们的吗？
Is that from them?

1267
01:29:33,550 --> 01:29:37,710
对，但别害怕 我想这是他们找我用的，仅此而已
Yeah. But don't be afraid. I think it's a way to find me, that's all.

1268
01:29:37,890 --> 01:29:41,580
你把他们带到这儿来？ 你让他们来对付自己人？
You led them here? You turned them on your own kind?

1269
01:29:42,390 --> 01:29:46,290
等等，你刚才不是说异形不存在吗？
Wait a second, you just said there's no such thing as aliens.

1270
01:29:48,730 --> 01:29:50,860
这个，当然不存在
Well, there's not.

1271
01:29:51,030 --> 01:29:54,660
就算存在 也只有叛变的傻瓜才会带他们来这儿
But if there were, only a traitorous fool would bring them here.

1272
01:29:54,840 --> 01:29:55,930
但他们必须来
But they have to come.

1273
01:29:56,100 --> 01:29:59,070
是他们抢走了我们的鱼 他们有办法解决的
They're the ones taking our fish. They can do something about it.

1274
01:29:59,240 --> 01:30:02,730
除了伟大的企鹅歌神之外 没人拥有给予和夺取的力量
None but the Great 'Guin has the power to give and take away.

1275
01:30:02,910 --> 01:30:07,370
但企鹅歌神并没有把事情变得如此反常 这是异形们干的
The Great 'Guin didn't put things out of whack, the aliens did.

1276
01:30:07,950 --> 01:30:11,890
这个白痴今天回来 是来取笑我们的苦难
A fool returns this day to mock our suffering.

1277
01:30:12,050 --> 01:30:16,180
我们正处于饥荒 他还要我们跟他一起跳
We are starving and he wants us to hippity-hop.

1278
01:30:16,360 --> 01:30:19,290
我们是坚持自己的生活方式…
So do we hold fast to our ways...

1279
01:30:19,460 --> 01:30:24,160
…还是会为这个跳舞白痴 荒诞的白日梦所蛊惑？
...or do we bend to the fetid fantasies of a dancing fool?

1280
01:30:32,970 --> 01:30:35,670
跟我说说，那个脚怎么跳来着？
Say, how does that feet thing go again?

1281
01:30:35,840 --> 01:30:37,400
对啊，给我们演示一下，曼波
Yeah, show us, Mumble.

1282
01:30:38,780 --> 01:30:40,840
哦，其实很简单
Oh, it's really quite easy.

1283
01:30:41,020 --> 01:30:42,640
不，不！
No, no!

1284
01:30:42,820 --> 01:30:44,150
不，你们必须抵制！
No, you must resist!

1285
01:30:44,990 --> 01:30:46,680
没错
That's right.

1286
01:30:47,060 --> 01:30:50,420
毫无意义的废话 抵制！原地站好！
Pointless nonsense. Resist! Stand your ground!

1287
01:30:50,590 --> 01:30:53,930
停止这荒唐的举动，站好！
Stand your ground against this folly!

1288
01:30:59,700 --> 01:31:02,760
放开嗓子，兄弟们
Raise your voices, brothers.

1289
01:31:02,940 --> 01:31:06,240
喊出你们对这些小丑的蔑视！
Cry out in defiance of this jiggity-joggity!

1290
01:31:06,410 --> 01:31:08,540
炫出你自己
Show me what you got.

1291
01:31:11,350 --> 01:31:13,080
对极了
You got it.

1292
01:31:17,620 --> 01:31:19,050
来吧
Come on.

1293
01:31:19,220 --> 01:31:20,550
好，继续
Work, work it.

1294
01:31:20,720 --> 01:31:23,820
没错，很好！让我们召唤智慧！
Yes, yes! Call on the wisdoms!

1295
01:31:23,990 --> 01:31:25,720
让大地颤抖！
Let the world tremble!

1296
01:31:26,160 --> 01:31:28,030
当别人都已离开…
For when all others leave...

1297
01:31:28,200 --> 01:31:30,060
…我们还在这！
...we remain!

1298
01:31:31,800 --> 01:31:33,430
曼波，曼波！
Mumble! Mumble!

1299
01:31:33,600 --> 01:31:36,400
妈妈？朋友们
Mama? Amigos.

1300
01:31:37,770 --> 01:31:40,610
哦，妈妈 哦，我的孩子
Oh, Mama. Oh, my boy.

1301
01:31:40,780 --> 01:31:43,370
我帅气的孩子 哦，妈妈
My gorgeous boy. Oh, Mama.

1302
01:31:43,550 --> 01:31:45,670
看看他 你是如此的耀眼
Look at him. You're so dazzling.

1303
01:31:45,850 --> 01:31:48,710
哦，毛球 我们一直在等你
Oh, Fluffy. We waited and waited for you.

1304
01:31:48,880 --> 01:31:51,720
噢，耶 爸在哪里？
Oh, yeah. Where's Pa?

1305
01:31:51,890 --> 01:31:54,150
相信我，你不会想看到你游手好闲的爸爸
Believe me. You don't wanna see your deadbeat dad.

1306
01:31:54,320 --> 01:31:56,380
你爸有点… 有点什么？
Your pa is sort of... What?

1307
01:31:56,560 --> 01:31:58,860
来吧，我领你去
Come on, I'll show you.

1308
01:32:08,240 --> 01:32:10,030
孟菲斯？
Memphis?

1309
01:32:11,070 --> 01:32:12,510
孟菲斯？
Memphis?

1310
01:32:12,670 --> 01:32:14,160
爸？
Pa?

1311
01:32:18,080 --> 01:32:19,710
曼波？
Mumble?

1312
01:32:19,880 --> 01:32:21,870
真的是你吗？
Is it truly you?

1313
01:32:22,050 --> 01:32:24,380
完完全全是我，爸
Every last bit of me, Pa.

1314
01:32:28,560 --> 01:32:30,390
我以为…
I thought...

1315
01:32:34,530 --> 01:32:36,020
爸？
Pa?

1316
01:32:39,630 --> 01:32:42,030
我对你做的那些事…
There ain't been one day...

1317
01:32:44,010 --> 01:32:48,640
…没有一件是正确的
...not one day, that I done right by you.

1318
01:32:52,980 --> 01:32:55,010
哦，爸
Oh, Pa.

1319
01:32:55,180 --> 01:32:57,050
为他跳舞吧，孩子他爸
Dance for him, Daddy.

1320
01:32:57,220 --> 01:32:59,210
跟孩子一起跳舞吧
Dance with your boy.

1321
01:33:02,560 --> 01:33:04,960
你必须原谅我
You'll have to forgive me.

1322
01:33:05,760 --> 01:33:08,820
我对音乐已经完全没感觉了
The music's gone clean out of me.

1323
01:33:10,700 --> 01:33:12,290
不，不会的
No, it hasn't.

1324
01:33:12,470 --> 01:33:16,270
这就像用身体唱歌
It's just like singing with your body.

1325
01:33:16,440 --> 01:33:18,460
来吧，爸爸，我们一起来
Come on, baby. We can do it.

1326
01:33:18,640 --> 01:33:20,200
哦，孩子他妈
Oh, Mama.

1327
01:33:20,380 --> 01:33:24,740
就是一只脚紧接着另一只脚动
It's just one big old foot after the other.

1328
01:33:30,150 --> 01:33:31,140
就这样
That's it.

1329
01:33:33,150 --> 01:33:34,990
是的
Yeah.

1330
01:33:36,360 --> 01:33:39,190
对，没错吧？ 嗯，感觉很好
Yeah, see? Well, that feels good.

1331
01:33:44,430 --> 01:33:47,870
想让我激情似火
You don't have to be beautiful

1332
01:33:48,300 --> 01:33:49,290
耶，孟菲斯
Yeah, Memphis.

1333
01:33:49,540 --> 01:33:51,160
不必在意外表
To turn me on

1334
01:33:51,640 --> 01:33:52,630
孩子他爸
Daddy.

1335
01:33:52,810 --> 01:33:56,830
我只需要你的身体，宝贝
I just need your body, baby

1336
01:33:57,010 --> 01:33:59,500
从日出到日落
From dusk till dawn

1337
01:34:00,720 --> 01:34:04,450
想成为我的女孩，不必多么富有
You don't have to be rich to be my girl

1338
01:34:04,620 --> 01:34:08,610
想主宰我的世界，不必特意装酷
You don't have to be cool To rule my world

1339
01:34:08,790 --> 01:34:12,690
没有比这，更适合我的歌曲
Ain't no particular song I'm more compatible with

1340
01:34:12,860 --> 01:34:17,530
我只是需要你更多的时间，还有…
I just want your extra time and your...

1341
01:34:37,850 --> 01:34:40,880
神圣的族群啊！
Holy flock!

1342
01:35:06,280 --> 01:35:08,720
妈呀，妈呀，妈呀
Mommy, Mommy, Mommy.

1343
01:35:45,390 --> 01:35:47,750
我想你现在最好开始跳舞
I think you better dance now.

1344
01:36:41,310 --> 01:36:43,780
一开始只有一只，现在是数以千计
First, there was just one. Now there's thousands.

1345
01:36:43,950 --> 01:36:46,640
它们是不是试图告诉我们什么？ 它们有什么问题？
Are they trying to tell us something? What's the problem?

1346
01:36:46,820 --> 01:36:49,610
我们搞乱了它们的食物链 我们必须做点什么
We're messing with their food chain. We've gotta do something.

1347
01:36:49,780 --> 01:36:53,480
我们建议禁止一切的海产捕捞 那么多利润，那么多工作机会
We suggest a ban on all marine harvesting. Too much money. Too many jobs.

1348
01:36:55,390 --> 01:36:57,550
我们到底为什么要那么做？
Why should we do anything at all?

1349
01:37:03,260 --> 01:37:06,630
它们只是这个世界的底层里 一群不会飞的鸟
They're just a bunch of flightless birds at the bottom of the world.

1350
01:37:11,140 --> 01:37:13,470
我可不想生活在没有企鹅的世界里
I don't wanna live in a world without penguins.

1351
01:37:13,640 --> 01:37:15,010
那我们该怎么办？
What are we gonna do about it?

1352
